Optional dependencies for Tkabber:
* audio/snack (sound notifications)
* graphics/tkimg (support for PNG, JPG images)
* net/tclmore (stream compression) [missing (https://gna.org/projects/tclmore/)]
* net/ztcl (stream compression) [missing (https://gna.org/projects/ztcl/)]
* security/tclgpg (encryption features) [missing (https://code.google.com/p/tclgpg/)]
* textproc/ispell (spell checking)
* x11/tkcon (Tk console)
* x11/tktray (iconify Tkabber)
* x11/xosd (OSD support)
